Note that 
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[ \begin {align*}  D_{\mathrm {KL}}(P || Q) &= \mathbb {E}_P \left [\log \left (\frac {P(x)}{Q(x)}\right )\right ] \\ &= \mathbb {E}_P \left [-\log \left (\frac {Q(x)}{P(x)}\right )\right ] \\ \end {align*} ]]></fr:tex>
